show.title: Batwara
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/8gGkSv
show.description: After 40 years of honest service as a railway ticket checker, a father’s retirement celebration turns bitter when his biological children abandon him and his wife. Humiliated and heartbroken, he finds strength in his adopted son and a forgotten book of poems that reveal the true meaning of love. A deeply emotional saga of sacrifice, betrayal, and the priceless bond that defines what family truly is.
